 of text varieties; phonetics/phonology; orthography; language acquisition.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 0aGerman languagexStudy and teachingxForeign speakers. 0aGerman philologyxStudy and teaching. 0aLinguistics. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / General.2bisacsh1 aAskedal, John Ole, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBarz, Irmhild, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBergerová, Hana, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBlei, Dagmar, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDalmas, Martine, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGärtner, Eberhard, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGötze, Lutz, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHennig, Mathilde, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHirschfeld, Ursula, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKempcke, Günter, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKubczak, Jacqueline, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMotsch, Wolfgang, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aReinecke, Werner, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSchröder, Jochen, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSchumacher, Helmut, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSkibitzki, Bernd, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aSommerfeldt, Karl-Ernst, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aStarke, Günter, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSuchsland, Peter, 